lock\" title=\"MARKETING SERVICES\" /></div>\r\n					<div class=\"side back\">\r\n						<p>SCLM backend modules serve multiple purposes. They can prove to be the best tool for communicating with your clients. Do you have something to share by email, push notification or text message? Easily create the content and send it out.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"light-grey-box\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<h1 class=\"center\">FEATURES OF SCLM</h1>\r\n			<div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n				<p><b>Increases your sales and profits</b></p>\r\n				<p><b>Custom design web ordering</b></p>\r\n				<p><b>Custom mobile ordering platform(iOS and Android)</b></p>\r\n				<p><b>Orders are printed directly as soonas submitted</b></p>\r\n				<p><b>Minimizes the human error</b></p>\r\n				<p><b>Allows faster service and better customer satisfaction</b></p>\r\n				<p><b>Instant update of the menu on all devices</b></p>\r\n				<p><b>Increases the value and higher brand awareness of your restaurants name</b></p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n				<p><b>Delivery Team Tracking</b><br /> Allows the real time location of the delivery team<br /> Shows the distance from the branch.<br /> Calculates the distance and time needed to reach the delivery destination.</p>\r\n				<p><b>Sales Reporting Module</b><br /> Analyzes sales by menu category and menu item<br /> Shows sales history by graphing mth/mth growth</p>\r\n				<p><b>Marketing Module</b><br /> Push Messaging<br /> SMS<br /> Email</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>','',1,2,'2016-10-13 11:01:01',754,'','2016-11-15 10:57:43',754,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2016-10-13 11:01:01','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}