g\" class=\"img-responsive center-block\" title=\"Social Media Consulting\" /></div>\r\n					<div class=\"side back\">\r\n						<p>Those brands choose us as their strategic partner. Our consulting practice works collaboratively with your in-house social media team to develop an overarching strategic direction and measurement plan up front. Were here to support you for long term, helping you apply and stay accountable to that strategy in an ever-changing space.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-xs-6\">\r\n			<div class=\"card-container\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"side medium-blue\">\r\n						<h3 class=\"center white\">Social Content Creation</h3>\r\n						<img src=\"/images/sales-tools/Full-Customer-Activity-History.png\" alt=\"Social Content Creation\" class=\"img-responsive center-block\" title=\"Social Content Creation\" /></div>\r\n					<div class=\"side back\">\r\n						<p>We create focused social media content that truly engages fans around your brand and products.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-xs-6\">\r\n			<div class=\"card-container\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"side light-blue\">\r\n						<h3 class=\"center white\">Promotions</h3>\r\n						<img src=\"/images/brand-management/psychological-pricing.png\" alt=\"Promotions\" class=\"img-responsive center-block\" title=\"Promotions\" /></div>\r\n					<div class=\"side back\">\r\n						<p>The goal of any promotion is to achieve the brands business objectives, and a well-planned and executed social media promotion does just that. The right program moves customers through the purchase loop and can turn customers into fans and fans into advocates.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>','',1,2,'2016-10-13 11:01:01',754,'','2016-11-15 07:24:15',754,754,'2016-11-15 08:47:14','2016-10-13 11:01:01','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\