cing. Most of today\'s CRM software fail when it comes to the distribution of the daily tasks and organizing deliveries. SIMPLU was developped to become a total collaboration tool between team members. It integrates several technologies that are essential for today\'s working style.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;SIMPLU\'s team strived to develop a modern platform using advanced web based technologies. It allows the data updates to be available instantly on your monitoring screen or mobile app.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Never miss an event. SIMPLU is empowered by a notification system which alerts for overdue tasks, tasks\' completion, geofencing...etc...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 style=&quot;color: #1b8ca6;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mobility&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;SIMPLU mobile application totally integrates with the back office web interface offering&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type: none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;A total synchronization of contacts, accounts and tasks databases.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;A task module which contains the tasks details, the contacts details including locations.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;A location module guides the field force to their destination.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;VOIP and chat capabilities are bundled to enhance communication and cut down on cost.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Total integration with existing IP PBX servers including asterisk.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 style=&quot;color: #1b8ca6;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manageability&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;SIMPLU\'s adminitrative interface is consisted of several modules tailored to address different industry verticals and working environments. SIMPLU supports businesses with multiple branches and departments.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;It consists of the modules listed below&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Employees&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Employee\'s working time sheet (on site check-in and check-out)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Employee\'s contact details and current on map location&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Employee\'s mobile application management&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Contacts&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Contacts full details including a primary and secondary on map locations&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Contacts assignment to employee for account management business model&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Accounts&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Accounts full details including a billing and shipping on map locations&nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Accounts management&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Tasks&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tasks creation and assignment to one or many employees&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tasks are enriched with the contacts details and location on map&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tasks synchronization with SIMPLU\'s mobile apps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tasks include a collaboration module allowing teams members to place notes and exchange files&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Ordering&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;This module is only available in SIMPLU FB. It allows the creation, editing of orders and a full interation with exisiting POS systems&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;VOIP call center module feature allowing the monitoring of the performance of the operators. It filters the incoming and outgoing calls by branches and departments. Real time statistics are calculated for performance assessment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Tracking&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Locate your team in real time in the tracking module&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Branches and task locations are published on the tracker map&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Be notified when your mobile force reaches their destination&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 style=&quot;color: #1b8ca6;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who benefits from SIMPLU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;SIMPLU mobile and back office applications integrate perfectly in&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Managed sales teams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Managed delivery teams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Ordering and delivery (SIMPLU FB)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Managed technical field force&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Transportation and fleet management&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; \n</pre></div>','',NULL,1,0,0,'2016-11-11 07:01:09','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,1,0,1,1,1,0,'','','','','','',NULL,'','en-GB',1,0,7,0,'easyblog.sitewide','81.196.107.209','ebd','{\"type\":\"ebd\",\"blocks\":[{\"uid\":\"011724177017915394\",\"type\":\"text\",\"html\":\"\\n            <p>Enter your text here ...<\\/p>        \",\"data\":{},\"blocks\":[],\"nested\":false,\"isolated\":false,\"text\":\"\\n            Enter your text here ...        \",\"editableHtml\":\"\\n            <div class=\\\"ebd-nest\\\" data-type=\\\"content\\\" data-eb-text-block-wrapper=\\\"\\\"><div class=\\\"ebd-block is-dropzone is-nested nest-right ui-droppable\\\" data-ebd-dropzone=\\\"\\\" data-ebd-dropzone-placeholder=\\\"\\\">\\n        <div>\\n            <span class=\\\"droptext\\\">Drop Blocks Here<\\/span>\\n        <\\/div>\\n    <\\/div><div class=\\\"ebd-block is-dropzone is-nested nest-left ui-droppable\\\" data-ebd-dropzone=\\\"\\\" data-ebd-dropzone-placeholder=\\\"\\\">\\n        <div>\\n            <span class=\\\"droptext\\\">Drop Blocks Here<\\/span>\\n        <\\/div>\\n    <\\/div><div data-content-type=\\\"html\\\" contenteditable=\\\"true\\\" data-eb-text-cont