3&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p&gt;SIMPLU mobile application totally integrates with the back office web interface offering&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n&lt;ul&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type: none;&quot;&gt;\\r\\n&lt;ul&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li&gt;A total synchronization of contacts, accounts and tasks databases.&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li&gt;A task module which contains the tasks details, the contacts details including locations.&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li&gt;A location module guides the field force to their destination.&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li&gt;VOIP and chat capabilities are bundled to enhance communication and cut down on cost.&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li&gt;Total integration with existing IP PBX servers including asterisk.&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;\\r\\n&lt;h3 style=&quot;color: #1b8ca6;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manageability&lt;\\/strong&gt;&lt;\\/h3&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;SIMPLU\'s adminitrative interface is consisted of several modules tailored to address different industry verticals and working environments. SIMPLU supports businesses with multiple branches and departments.&nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p&gt;It consists of the modules listed below&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;\\r\\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6&quot;&gt;\\r\\n&lt;h4&gt;Employees&lt;\\/h4&gt;\\r\\n&lt;ul&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li&gt;Employee\'s working time sheet (on site check-in and check-out)&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li&gt;Employee\'s contact details and current on map location&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li&gt;Employee\'s mobile application management&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;\\r\\n&lt;br \\/&gt;\\r\\n&lt;h4&gt;Contacts&lt;\\/h4&gt;\\r\\n&lt;ul&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li&gt;Contacts full details including a primary and secondary on map locations&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;li&gt;Contacts assignment to employee for account management business model&lt;\\/li&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;\\r\\n&lt;br \\/&gt;\\r\\n&lt;h4&gt;Accounts&lt;\\/h4&gt;\\r\\n&lt;ul&gt;\\r