ext-align: justify;\\\\\\\">SIMPLU\'s adminitrative interface is consisted of several modules tailored to address different industry verticals and working environments. SIMPLU supports businesses with multiple branches and departments.&nbsp;<\\\\\\/p>\\\\n<p>It consists of the modules listed below<\\\\\\/p>\\\\n<div class=\\\\\\\"row\\\\\\\">\\\\n<div class=\\\\\\\"col-md-6\\\\\\\">\\\\n<h4>Employees<\\\\\\/h4>\\\\n<ul>\\\\n<li>Employee\'s working time sheet (on site check-in and check-out)<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<li>Employee\'s contact details and current on map location<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<li>Employee\'s mobile application management<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<\\\\\\/ul>\\\\n<br>\\\\n<h4>Contacts<\\\\\\/h4>\\\\n<ul>\\\\n<li>Contacts full details including a primary and secondary on map locations<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<li>Contacts assignment to employee for account management business model<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<\\\\\\/ul>\\\\n<br>\\\\n<h4>Accounts<\\\\\\/h4>\\\\n<ul>\\\\n<li>Accounts full details including a billing and shipping on map locations&nbsp;<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<li>Accounts management<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<\\\\\\/ul>\\\\n<br>\\\\n<h4>Tasks<\\\\\\/h4>\\\\n<ul>\\\\n<li>Tasks creation and assignment to one or many employees<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<li>Tasks are enriched with the contacts details and location on map<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<li>Tasks synchronization with SIMPLU\'s mobile apps<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<li>Tasks include a collaboration module allowing teams members to place notes and exchange files<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<\\\\\\/ul>\\\\n<\\\\\\/div>\\\\n<div class=\\\\\\\"col-md-6\\\\\\\">\\\\n<h4>Ordering<\\\\\\/h4>\\\\n<ul>\\\\n<li>This module is only available in SIMPLU FB. It allows the creation, editing of orders and a full interation with exisiting POS systems<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<li>VOIP call center module feature allowing the monitoring of the performance of the operators. It filters the incoming and outgoing calls by branches and departments. Real time statistics are calculated for performance assessment<\\\\\\/li>\\\\n<\