 for performance assessment<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\n<h4>Tracking<\\/h4>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Locate your team in real time in the tracking module<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Branches and task locations are published on the tracker map<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Be notified when your mobile force reaches their destination<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: #1b8ca6;\\\"><strong>Who benefits from SIMPLU<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>SIMPLU mobile and back office applications integrate perfectly in\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Managed sales teams<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Managed delivery teams<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Ordering and delivery (SIMPLU FB)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Managed technical field force<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Transportation and fleet management<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"blocks\":[],\"nested\":false,\"isolated\":false,\"text\":\"\",\"editableHtml\":\"\\n            <pre data-mode=\\\"javascript\\\">function foobar() {\\n    \\/\\/ Write some codes here\\n}<\\/pre>        \"}],\"version\":\"1.0\"}\";s:8:\"category\";s:15:\"Technical Stuff\";s:6:\"author\";s:10:\"Super User\";s:16:\"created_by_alias\";s:10:\"Super User\";s:9:\"cat_state\";s:1:\"1\";s:10:\"cat_access\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"metakay\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"metadesc\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"layout\";s:5:\"entry\";s:4:\"path\";s:37:\"index.php/en-blog/let-s-get-technical\";s:7:\"summary\";s:24:\"Enter your text here ...\";s:4:\"body\";s:5006:\"<div class=\"ebd-block \" data-type=\"text\" ><p>Enter your text here ...</p></div><div class=\"ebd-block \" data-type=\"code\" ><pre id=\"58256fb91d16a\" class=\"eb-block-code\">\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;SIMPLU is based on a customer relationship management platform, enhanced with geolocation and geofencing. Most of today\'s CRM software fail when it comes to the distribution of the daily tasks and organizing deliveries. SIMPLU was developped to becom