purpose.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A website must always consider the end user. User-friendliness can be achieved by paying attention to the following factors: navigation, multimedia, compatibility, technology, interactivity. We create excellent User Interface (UI) Design, for a satisfying web experience for your clients, planning and analysing, paying attention to individual client specifications, converting the design process into a beautiful experience for everyone.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>Responsive Web Design<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>So, many of us would ask; what is responsive website design? Well, this is a new method of website design which makes use of the latest technologies and frameworks in web design such as html5, css3 media queries, and JavaScript to solve the headache of having to design different versions of the same website for different devices.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Having a proficient and experienced team of web developers and web designers we offer all kinds of designing specialties across different niches. All our web designing solutions come with service excellence like on-time delivery, high-quality code and persistent support after the job is done.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p><br class=\\\"hidden-xs\\\" \\/><br class=\\\"hidden-xs\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"container\\\">\\r\\n<h1 class=\\\"center\\\">our portfolio<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h3 class=\\\"center\\\">Have a look at our latest website designs<\\/h3>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"container\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"col-sm-4\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"center\\\" style=\\\"border: 1px solid #000; padding: 1%; margin-bottom: 3%;\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/sclm.ro\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/portfolio\\/sclm.png\\\" alt=\\\"sclm\\\" class=\\\"img-responsive center-block\\\" title=\\\"SCLM\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h1>sclm.ro<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"color: #0088b3; text-transform: none; font-weight: 400 !important;\\\">Ordering